Summary: walking down street,dark,glanced up and there it was ,gliding 150 ft over my head
divs: Sighting Detailsi was walking my dog this morning down the street,i glanced up and saw a boomerang shaped craft,60 or 70 feet,wingtip to wingtip,about 150 ft over head.it was gliding,no noise,it seemed to pause for a few secs and then glided off.my dog barked at it.it also seemed to reflect the area below it.i was amazed.thats all.i live on the intercoastal waterway,if that matters.
